{"tid":749302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<華為p20 pro> 真實用家，幾個月後用後感 (無圖)","createTime":"2018-07-20T02:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T04:21:24.000Z","uid":137220,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"597879f78abb5afe3fb5d59ed0458eec453da7e4","tid":749302,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T02:18:17.000Z","msg":"打手死全家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好，先講結論 - 唔值得<br />\n當時買6千幾黎講，應該有更好選擇掛?<br />\n<br />\n佢無明顯致命缺點，呢個價位黎講我認為係有D令人失望<br />\n<br />\n劣勢如下:<br />\n1.Mon偏黃嚴重，較到最冷色都係黃，剛上手係睇唔慣<br />\n<br />\n2.相機味精太重，尤其是影人自拍。就算無開美顏，無開人像mode都好似用左咁<br />\n<br />\n3.通話時用擴音收得差，語音打字detect得差。用呢兩個功能我要要痴近個收音(係電話頂)<br />\n令我覺得個咪係比較渣<br />\n<br />\n4. earphone一定要用usbc，加個轉插係有D煩，不過呢個係已知規格，算係小問題....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其餘功能不過不失啦，反應算快，仲未變慢，無野壞<br />\n影相(非自拍)係比同期手機清晰D ge，但可能都係味精重<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而我諗到佢明顯優勢就得一樣，就係影夜景/黑暗環境<br />\n<br />\n其他手機係呢個光度影一定係noise/乜7都影唔到<br />\n但我剛用佢試影係比佢嚇左一跳，光/清到好唔真實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f57114946deb2dc9f7041f1d183da2622a64b44","tid":749302,"uid":20815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"6千幾買大陸機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1a693fc24efe9b5db752dc04aad2bdc3ee8660","tid":749302,"uid":154787,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f57114946deb2dc9f7041f1d183da2622a64b44","tid":749302,"uid":20815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"6千幾買大陸機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so